  "texts": [
    "Figure 14 provides statistics on 103 instruction fine-tuning datasets from six aspects: release time, license, data category, construction method, language, and domain.",
    "The following conclusion can be drawn:",
    "(1) The number of instruction fine-tuning datasets is showing a growing trend.",
    "The widespread attention to LLMs and the application of the instruction fine-tuning paradigm have greatly facilitated the construction and open-sourcing of instruction fine-tuning datasets.",
    "The demand for model fine-tuning and research interest in this area are rapidly expanding."
  ]
}